    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0889b22"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date>越州妙喜寺<persName key="A013839">僧達</persName>傳</head><p>
<lb ed="T" n="0889b23"/><persName key="A013839">釋僧達</persName>，姓王氏，<placeName key="CN0330602Z02AA">會稽</placeName>人也。稚齒英奇，不參
<lb ed="T" n="0889b24"/>戲弄，於龜山<placeName key="CN0330621T04AA">妙喜道場</placeName>出俗。<placeName key="CN0330621T04AA">其寺</placeName><date key="j19045331909604" notAfter-iso="0516" notBefore-iso="0502">南梁</date>初
<lb ed="T" n="0889b25"/>建。後樂遊方，見<persName key="A000237">黃梅忍禪師</persName>，若枯苗得雨，
<lb ed="T" n="0889b26"/>隨順修禪，罔有休懈。遇<persName key="A009251">印宗禪師</persName>，重磨心
        <lb ed="T" n="0889b27"/>鑑。<placeName key="CN0411526Z16AA">光州</placeName>見<persName key="A008876">道岸律師</persName>，更勵律儀。四眾<ptr target="#n98"/>依歸，
<lb ed="T" n="0889b28"/>如水宗海。<date key="j19617861961814" notAfter-iso="0659-03-01" notBefore-iso="0659-02-01">開元七年</date>示疾而終，春秋八十
<lb ed="T" n="0889b29"/>二云。</p>
